  <summary date="2019-02-01T15:44:09Z" status="Introduced in House">Secure Every Child Under the Right Equipment Standards Act of 2018 or the SECURES Act of 2018

This bill directs the Department of Transportation to publish a notice of proposed rulemaking on new federal standards for school bus seat belt requirements on all school buses, regardless of gross vehicle weight rating.</summary>
